&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Excitation+ (E+) or VCC is red&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Excitation- (E-) or ground is black.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Output+ (O+), Signal+ (S+)+ or Amplifier+ (A+) is white&lt;/li>
&lt;li>O-, S-, or A- is green or blue&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
